---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import DarkContentShell from '@/components/DarkContentShell.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <DarkContentShell>
    <h1 slot="title" class="mb-10 text-center text-4xl font-cyber text-accent">
      Terms & Conditions
    </h1>

    <p class="mb-6 font-mono tracking-[1.2px] text-white/80">
      These Terms and Conditions govern your use of the website operated by F.A.S. Motorsports
      ("Company", "we", "our", or "us"), located at fasmotorsports.com, and any products or
      services offered through it. By accessing or using this website, you agree to be bound by
      these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the site.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-2 text-2xl font-cyber text-white">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 font-mono tracking-[1.2px] text-white/75">
      By using our website and purchasing our services or products, you confirm that you are at
      least 18 years of age and legally capable of entering into binding contracts.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-2 text-2xl font-cyber text-white">2. Modifications</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 font-mono tracking-[1.2px] text-white/75">
      We reserve the right to change these Terms and Conditions at any time without prior notice.
      Your continued use of the website constitutes your acceptance of any changes.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-2 text-2xl font-cyber text-white">3. SMS Communications</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 font-mono tracking-[1.2px] text-white/75">
      By opting in to receive SMS communications, employees and authorized users consent to receive
      transactional, operational text messages related to internal business activity. These
      messages may include notifications regarding new orders, vendor or customer messages,
      appointment requests, or other time-sensitive system alerts.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4 font-mono tracking-[1.2px] text-white/75">
      SMS communications are not used for marketing or promotional purposes. Message frequency
      varies based on operational activity. Recipients may opt out at any time by replying STOP.
      For assistance, reply HELP or contact support@fasmotorsports.com.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-2 text-2xl font-cyber text-white">4. Performance Products Disclaimer</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 font-mono tracking-[1.2px] text-white/75">
      All performance parts and tuning services are intended for off-road or track use only. Use of
      aftermarket parts may void factory warranties and violate local emissions laws. It is the
      buyer’s responsibility to ensure compliance.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-2 text-2xl font-cyber text-white">5. No Warranties</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 font-mono tracking-[1.2px] text-white/75">
      All products and services are sold “as is.” F.A.S. Motorsports does not offer any warranties,
      express or implied. Any risk associated with use or installation of parts is assumed solely
      by the purchaser.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-2 text-2xl font-cyber text-white">6. Returns & Refunds</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 font-mono tracking-[1.2px] text-white/75">
      Please refer to our <a
        href="https://fasmotorsports.com/returnRefundPolicy"
        class="text-accent underline decoration-accent/70 underline-offset-4 hover:text-white"
        >Refund & Returns Policy</a
      > for information regarding product returns.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-2 text-2xl font-cyber text-white">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 font-mono tracking-[1.2px] text-white/75">
      F.A.S. Motorsports shall not be held liable for any damages, injury, or loss arising from the
      use or inability to use our products or services. This includes but is not limited to vehicle
      damage, voided warranties, and loss of performance.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-2 text-2xl font-cyber text-white">8. Governing Law</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 font-mono tracking-[1.2px] text-white/75">
      These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Florida. Any disputes arising out of
      these Terms shall be handled in the appropriate courts of Florida.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-2 text-2xl font-cyber text-white">9. Contact Information</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 font-mono tracking-[1.2px] text-white/75">
      For any questions regarding these Terms and Conditions, please contact us at <a
        href="mailto:support@fasmotorsports.com"
        class="text-accent underline decoration-accent/70 underline-offset-4 hover:text-white"
        >support@fasmotorsports.com</a
      >.
    </p>
  </DarkContentShell>
</BaseLayout>
